what is Api:-
*****************
Api stands ofr Appliction programming interface 
Api is a mechanism by using which one type Appliction can communicate whith Another
Appliction.
In general api is very big topic 

Api are used by defferent Appliction to data from one platefrom to another platefrom
worldmeter .com corona virus Api
any Appliction A,B,C,D,E,F,G can utilise the Api of worldmeter.com to get live update of corona.

1..interoperability : conversion of one type of language to soeme common language so that data con be exchange without derectly 
conerting the one language to another language

Interoperability refers to shoarig of data from one Appliction to Another Appliction
without changeing native language ,by means of some common Intercoversion language
or 
sharing of data from one App to another App without derectly coverting native language is called interoperability.


for Eg:
Android --->json--->java
python --->json--->java
python --->json--->php
php --->json--->SQL

maain feature of interoperability is platefrom indepent native.

php-->(serialisation/json Encoding )-->json ---(Deseriasation/json Decode)->SQL
serialisation/json Encoding : converting one type PL. to JSON object
Deseriasation/json Decode : converting JSON type to one type data-type of PL

EG:
php---> json_decde() ---->json (serialiation)
Associativ Array  ----> json 

json ---> json_decode() ---> Associativ Array. (De-serialiation) 

what is web-service.:-any type of service over the internet  is termed as web-service,  it can be any type
of service and can use any protocol.


what is web-Api.:-
the Api which can be accessed only via web interface internet as a medium  is called
as web-Api
