what is soap.:--
it is type of web-Api which can used be used, to transport data/represent the data ,in fromSimpaleobject Access protocal which used 
XML DAta representation.

Eg:
<XML:nmps="version/XML-document-4">
		<xml:Envelope>
		       <Employee>
					<user id="1">
								<email><sudhir@gmail.com</email>
								<passwrod>1234</passwrod>
						</user>
					</Employee>	
				</Envelope>
</xml>
used for very heavy data transmission.
Soap is highly Scalable
Soap is secure, why because you access nth node for access real node 
Soap Architecture can very very deep that it can be very complex to handle
				

